  "transcription_segments": [
    {
      "id": "c88da189-8945-4ebd-8e23-f6594416f592",
      "speaker_discord_id": "420362662208339968",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Agora é pra ser um teste final do bloco de 5 minutos, nós iremos colocar faroeste caboclo no bote de música pra ver o que ele vai gravar tudo aqui, me aguarde!",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 0.18,
      "timestamp_end": 17.18,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:30.559000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:47.559000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "0b2c4256-b6f5-4052-b76a-1e99ba0e6d5f",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não tinha medo de estar ajudando o santo que isso era o que todos diziam quando ele se perdeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 7.02,
      "timestamp_end": 10.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:37.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:40.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "4a365c2c-5b9e-4c95-9276-68ab160fe593",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Deixou pra trás tudo uma asa na fazenda só pra assistir no seu santo e o outro que já se viveu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 10.02,
      "timestamp_end": 13.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:40.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:43.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "680a52e8-4b80-4791-8d83-650e3dc080fb",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Quando criança só pensava em ser bandido ainda mais do que um tiro se soltava pra morrer",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 13.02,
      "timestamp_end": 16.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:43.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:46.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6971b94d-736c-4ecf-8ccc-5544badc83a0",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Era o terror da serra minha onde morava e na escola até o professor como ele aprendeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 16.02,
      "timestamp_end": 18.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:46.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:48.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "9d02f6d8-3dee-4bdd-a59b-fcc04e80b0e8",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E a cabeça só pra roubar o dinheiro que as alunas colocavam na caixinha do altar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 18.02,
      "timestamp_end": 21.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:48.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:51.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "4a7e6421-0484-4bf6-913b-61bd9bc18968",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Sentia mesmo que era mesmo diferente, sentia que aquilo ali não era o seu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 21.02,
      "timestamp_end": 24.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:51.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:54.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "bea9e9f3-a401-48d3-90e8-1124ccb16e7f",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele queria sair para ver o mar, olha as forças que ele via na televisão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 24.02,
      "timestamp_end": 27.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:54.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:57:57.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "f2e9f0ba-db75-4554-877e-81d03f660c16",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Chegou dinheiro para poder lhe achar, escolheu a prova, escolheu a solidão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 27.02,
      "timestamp_end": 30.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:57:57.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:00.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "f5fdcb6c-cfc8-4bfa-bdee-016e215140b6",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Comia todas as meninas, a cidade de santo, liga de médico, a sozinha e o professor",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 30.02,
      "timestamp_end": 33.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:00.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:03.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "df063eef-b3cc-4bad-a598-8887d6f758ec",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Eles foram mandados pro reclamatório, o diabo mandou um swatch que acha que tanto que errou",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 33.02,
      "timestamp_end": 35.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:03.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:05.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b16f1cea-e142-4911-9037-e8bcf8fed29a",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não entendi é como a vida funcionava, as inquilinas são causadas pela sua cor",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 35.02,
      "timestamp_end": 38.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:05.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:08.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e3a31993-391a-461e-a729-6281efd33a6f",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ficou cansado de detar, achar respostas, comprou uma passagem, foi direto pra Salvador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 38.02,
      "timestamp_end": 41.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:08.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:11.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "70d3686f-c65a-435f-9fcc-8b80d434c312",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E vai chegando foi tomar um cafezinho, foi um boiadeiro que tinha que falar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 41.02,
      "timestamp_end": 44.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:11.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:14.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1ffa0d5f-c58b-4d17-861f-9b3ca1b16e41",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E o boiadeiro tinha uma passagem, ia perder a viagem, mas foi salvar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 44.02,
      "timestamp_end": 47.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:14.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:17.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "88625db9-de19-4de9-bdd1-32db9986eafb",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Dizia ele, estou vindo pra Brasília, nesse país o que é melhor não há",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 47.02,
      "timestamp_end": 49.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:17.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:19.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "5aba46f4-27c3-4d63-822e-1cc90299fbf7",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Tô precisando visitar a minha filha, eu vim com a filha e você tá em meu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 49.02,
      "timestamp_end": 52.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:19.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:22.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "94786e5d-2bbc-46ad-b361-375c50676987",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E quando você consuma da bola de um ônibus e o trono tá no central",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 52.02,
      "timestamp_end": 55.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:22.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:25.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "5929fb42-10f5-4c75-8652-4d9f44cb7f48",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Ele ficou vestido, o cara quase caça, ele falou que ia ver os luzes de natal",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 55.02,
      "timestamp_end": 58.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:25.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:28.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "057b7194-1281-44e7-afc3-50a7c37bab67",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O que é isso que tá de linda?",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 58.02,
      "timestamp_end": 59.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:28.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:29.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6bd4450c-52b8-44da-90d8-0882f1cf1097",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O outro reconoce a falada",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 59.02,
      "timestamp_end": 61.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:29.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:31.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "a0ebe556-a7f7-407b-9432-bfad6e1c1bbc",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Pra mangueira verde de cartilha, nasce a filha, nasce a batida",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 61.02,
      "timestamp_end": 63.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:31.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:33.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6cb0f10c-2176-4620-ab33-e121a2ecf284",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Nasce a filha, faz uma das casca, sacou seus filhos, o rapaz trabalhou",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 63.02,
      "timestamp_end": 66.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:33.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:36.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b541ed08-1efd-4e94-8de6-78e354815783",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E conhecia muita gente dele, só não tinha o mesmo papel do seu filho",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 66.02,
      "timestamp_end": 68.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:36.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:38.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "7aa1be3a-a2ba-4c9c-bec5-76f921483fb9",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Só vou ver o anjo que vivia na Colívia",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 68.02,
      "timestamp_end": 70.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:38.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:40.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "df3a1531-08c0-4751-8da4-a3e2023a1568",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Aí muitas pessoas iam se adivar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 70.02,
      "timestamp_end": 72.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:40.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:42.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e30fe7a4-4c9f-4b05-a6c7-cb48ee72ad66",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Se não via a fábrica, via o negócio e ia conversar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 72.02,
      "timestamp_end": 74.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:42.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:44.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1af34655-f909-44da-acbb-d2c171f14d4d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Só quis ver a moscada, lá na manteiga, eu mandava dele se adiantar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 74.02,
      "timestamp_end": 77.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:44.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:47.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "05925ad9-5596-4461-a625-cccaec90a3c6",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Eu via as sete horas do oficial, eles se cresciam e os sonhos iam se adiantar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 77.02,
      "timestamp_end": 80.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:47.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:50.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "78eae77d-91e0-47df-8268-4d189c01ebb8",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Mas se ele não viria mais pés que existir, o compaco dele ia se virar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 80.02,
      "timestamp_end": 82.02,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:58:50.399000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:58:52.399000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "77395434-c556-4e92-9bb1-cf063501536c",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Essas palavras conectaram o coração",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 309.62,
      "timestamp_end": 311.16,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T19:02:39.999000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T19:02:41.539000+00:00",
